data.description: Great home in Castle Rock!  Clean home with a great location! Newer paint, Huge fenced in yard with a large covered patio! This open floorplan is a great starter home. Nice corner lot with just one neighbor. This house has a large 2 car garage  and updated fixtures. The end home has a larger lot with extra space for entertaining.  Great price for a great home this one wont last long!!
